    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Final Verdict</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      The Bahamas BEATS program offers paradise at a premium. The $25 visa is the cheapest entry ticket to any digital nomad destination, but the cost of living makes this a high-income destination.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      For remote workers earning $6,000+/month who want crystal-clear Caribbean waters, zero income tax, English-speaking culture, and quick access to the US, the Bahamas delivers an exceptional lifestyle.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6">
      The tradeoffs are clear: high costs, limited healthcare requiring evacuation coverage, and hurricane exposure. If your income supports it, the Bahamas offers a tropical paradise just 50 miles from Miami.
    </p>

